#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Phone" field of the "Staff" table</h2>
This field is the primary phone number for this staff member.  If at all possible, it should also
be able to receive texts, but it should always be able to take phone calls.
<p>
It is in the form:
<div class=field_format>(nnn)nnn-nnnn</div>

<p>Note that if you just type in the digits, it will rewrite it to that form. 


